snippet.title: Live Coding: Learning Angular Framework
snippet.description:
Angular is a popular framework for creating user interfaces. Let's dive in and learn how it works so we can compare it to React. We'll start from scratch learning how to install it and working through a tutorial. Then we'll look at how to package and do some basic tasks.
